  "projectName": "WP SSR Framework",
  "projectDescription": "A headless static-hybrid WordPress framework that renders a React SPA through server-side controllers, with a built-in router, Eloquent-style ORM for custom post types, SSG caching, SEO management, and a REST API layer — all running as a WordPress mu-plugin on top of Bedrock.",
