  "keyFeatures": [
    "Headless WordPress with a custom PHP controller-based web router that intercepts requests before theme rendering",
    "Static Site Generator (SSG) that renders pages to HTML via an external headless browser API and serves them to bots",
    "Eloquent-style ORM (EloquentCPT) wrapping WordPress custom post types with a fluent QueryBuilder",
    "ACF Pro integration for structured custom post type fields defined entirely in PHP",
    "REST API router registering custom endpoints under /api/v1 via the WordPress REST API",
    "React 19 + Vite SPA loaded as the frontend, with server-injected window.__wp_data__ and soft navigation",
    "Built-in SEO management with ACF fields, per-post score tracking, and an admin dashboard",
    "Plausible Analytics integration embedded directly in the WordPress admin",
    "Service provider system for modular bootstrapping (routing, cache, SEO, SSG, analytics, rate limiting)",
    "WP-CLI commands: eloquent:generate and pages:sync",
    "Telegram notifications for new contact / quote form submissions",
    "Bedrock-based project structure with Composer dependency management and dotenv configuration"
  ],
